➜90后研究生用周杰伦专辑为5亿年前三叶虫命名：范特西虫
http://www.sohu.com/a/434621928_260616	1762
<div id="sohuplayer">
<script type="text/javascript" src="//tv.sohu.com/upload/swf/showVrsPlayer.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript">
showVrsPlayer({
bid:'225612161',
width: '500',
height: '375',
autoplay: false,
